    ul
      li Choose your project
      li Come up with a broad description of what it will look like when its done
      li Write everything down somewhere (paper, notepad++, etc)

  section
    h2 Project Design
    ul
      li 
        | Once you have a solid idea, start to flesh out the project more
        ul
          li 
            | For structures
            ul
              li Draw your shapes on paper 
              li Label their heights
              li Mark what blocks they will use
          li
